Text: Salmon Energy Escrow Agreementemail is confidential and may well also be legally privileged If you have received it in error you are on notice of its status Please notify us immediately by reply email and then delete this message from your system Please do not copy it or use it for any purposes or disclose its contents to any other person to do so could be a breach of confidence Thank you for your cooperation Please contact our IT Helpdesk on Ext or email if you need assistance Attached please find the comments of Delta Power and the lenders to the Escrow Agreement Please do not hesitate to call Gregg or me to discuss these comments Scannedpdf
